{"tid":1265880,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[擺明hea做 吹咩?]《精靈寶可夢》 製作人增田順一開腔回應 過半小精靈不能使用大炎上事件","createTime":"2019-06-29T11:52:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T01:13:01.000Z","uid":75050,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"31da7fec7c9e49e2fe4d81dcf645f07a5680941c","tid":1265880,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T11:52:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://greatgame.asia/《精靈寶可夢》大炎上事件-製作人增田順一開腔回/?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgreatgame.asia%2F%E3%80%8A%E7%B2%BE%E9%9D%88%E5%AF%B6%E5%8F%AF%E5%A4%A2%E3%80%8B%E5%A4%A7%E7%82%8E%E4%B8%8A%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6-%E8%A3%BD%E4%BD%9C%E4%BA%BA%E5%A2%9E%E7%94%B0%E9%A0%86%E4%B8%80%E9%96%8B%E8%85%94%E5%9B%9E%2F%3F&d=FYZ0PdCaIZeH%2BWUkJYSmq3HDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=5004f86d\" target=\"_blank\">https://greatgame.asia/《精靈寶可夢》大炎上事件-製作人增田順一開腔回/?</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>《精靈寶可夢》大炎上事件 製作人增田順一開腔回應！</ins></strong><br />\n游雲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imagizer.imageshack.com/img922/925/KXHsx1.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimagizer.imageshack.com%2Fimg922%2F925%2FKXHsx1.jpg%3F&h=7aa73292&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信不少玩家都有留意《精靈寶可夢》的炎上事件了吧！這事件源於即於11月15日於Switch推出新一代的《精靈寶可夢 劍/盾》中，不能繼承使用回舊世代的小精靈，以致很多小精靈在「Pokemon Home」內形同「坐監」。<br />\n<br />\n在這個消息傳出外，有部份粉絲完全覺得很不合理，繼而令遊戲的視頻負評不斷。在這樣的一遍反對聲音之下，負責遊戲開發的Game Freak製作人增田順一，今日終於在《精靈寶可夢 劍/盾》的美國官方網站上，對廣大的粉絲的訴求開腔回應，以下為翻譯的版本。<br />\n<br />\n相關聲明網站連結<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pokemon.com/us/a-message-for-pokemon-video-game-fans/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pokemon.com%2Fus%2Fa-message-for-pokemon-video-game-fans%2F&d=FYZ0PdCaIZeH%2BWUkJYSmq3HDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=a9a852c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pokemon.com/us/a-message-for-pokemon-video-game-fans/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>非常感謝一直支持及愛護《精靈寶可夢》的粉絲，早前宣佈了無法將一部份小精靈轉移至《精靈寶可夢 劍/盾》的消息，我看到了大家對此事的評論及見解，亦深深感受到大家對這款作品的愛。<br />\n<br />\n跟大家一樣，我們也十分珍惜《精靈寶可夢》，我們也跟大家一樣對每一款小精靈也相當上心，我本人一直參與《精靈寶可夢》系列的開發工作，因此要作這個決斷時我也感到很艱難，在此我想跟各位熱愛這款遊戲的粉絲說一聲，那些還未在《精靈寶可夢 劍/盾》登場的小精靈，並不代表未來不會在後續的作品中登場。<br />\n<br />\n將來，《精靈寶可夢》的世界將會變得更廣闊，在伽勒爾地區遇上新的小精靈，與未曾見過的訓練員對戰，開啟一個令人期待全新的冒險。我們仍會全心全意打造一款令玩家感到快樂的作品，因此希望各位能對本作品有所期待。</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n以上就是整個聲明的原文翻譯，簡單一點而言，就是今次製作人的公佈，其實是表示雖然今次《精靈寶可夢 劍/盾》未能收錄所有小精靈，但不久的將來其他的《精靈寶可夢》中，是有可能看到牠們的身影啊！<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀:<br />\n<strong><ins>[賺咁多都係要偷懶]《寶可夢》公司5年收益上漲12倍 吸金能力令人瞠目</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1261984/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1261984/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>[Switch] 《精靈寶可夢 劍/盾》一半以上小精靈不能使用！大炎上！史無前例負評如潮！</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1251380/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1251380/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"a6df9f50c213d132ab86f358617659e2cc8bf533","tid":1265880,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T12:01:44.000Z","msg":"後續的作品<br />\n<br />\n即係劍盾唔會有啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0171d6cc81d7d72cf7d7ee24f4bc2c95fddbba02","tid":1265880,"uid":7043,"like":15,"dislike":7,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T12:12:41.000Z","msg":"由佢改左名做寶可夢開始<br />\n就知呢間野根本唔抵買<br />\n擺玩啦"},{"pid":"fe2677250e4783d7108e1dd64287167ba5b09f5e","tid":1265880,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"a6df9f50c213d132ab86f358617659e2cc8bf533","tid":1265880,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T12:01:44.000Z","msg":"後續的作品<br />\n<br />\n即係劍盾唔會有啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T13:34:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da6598967f04b10c44d1dd35a1c22c33cff1c19c","tid":1265880,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T14:38:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b03623105f29c54f97488a73691920c75cee59e7","tid":1265880,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T14:40:05.000Z","msg":"咪又係大賣"},{"pid":"f0dc88f59f1915305897e8c2d20b406523efb984","tid":1265880,"uid":235152,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:08:55.000Z","msg":"佢地立場勁硬頸,示威公開信出過都當你傻,你唔洗指意會改,乖乖地課金買任豚"},{"pid":"c17248ab2339d92588c602d3a30a4fdff515cf89","tid":1265880,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T18:05:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f6ab7358f0a8d985970308b5ccf9f66d89c5f0f","tid":1265880,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T23:22:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98bba2f3968cd6da6397a57e61c03c5b8d6bb40b","tid":1265880,"uid":187972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T23:31:33.000Z","msg":"増田順一，林鄭月娥<br />\n為何驚人相似？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b68993cd152e93a6bc0d4f60c31012d6b5e3b7b","tid":1265880,"uid":49078,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T23:32:24.000Z","msg":"冇咪冇囉 點講我都會照買架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c4de31ccdb529b3e21040e1657c6de3596e5ea8","tid":1265880,"uid":30468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T00:01:25.000Z","msg":"由紅版開始集集都有玩<br />\n不過今次會缺席啦"},{"pid":"dd98296bdf2de8027739895ff7ba6628094073a8","tid":1265880,"uid":56063,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T00:08:17.000Z","msg":"唔會買<br />\n唔會玩<br />\n唔會理<br />\n<br />\n佢話cut pokemon開始就無再睇過劍盾嘅嘢<br />\n完全失去晒興趣"},{"pid":"42d9dda4fb69d3263680651c0899b7584803643a","tid":1265880,"uid":75050,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd98296bdf2de8027739895ff7ba6628094073a8","tid":1265880,"uid":56063,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T00:08:17.000Z"